{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775853822086,"sessionID":"ses_286df9283ffeyWNoEXHArL2IDP","part":{"id":"prt_d7920f2980010vJSr0djC51ZAC","messageID":"msg_d7920d8fa001Tn44I92suGowxU","sessionID":"ses_286df9283ffeyWNoEXHArL2IDP","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_27dab9dcbabb4abf89753a2f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-022 — CLI publish 命令\n\n**Module:** cmd/cli\n**Language:** Python\n**Size:** L\n\n## 目的\n\n为 AgentCube CLI (`kubectl-agentcube`) 实现 `publish` 子命令，将已构建的 Agent 镜像发布/部署到目标环境。支持两种 provider 模式：`agentcube`（部署 AgentRuntime Custom Resource 到 Kubernetes）和 `k8s`（部署标准 Deployment + NodePort Service）。`publish` 命令负责准备镜像（本地 Docker push 或使用已有 image URL）、创建/更新 Kubernetes 资源、等待部署就绪，并将发布结果持久化回 `agent_metadata.yaml`。\n\n当前 Python CLI 已定义 `publish` 命令的 Typer 签名和 `PublishRuntime` 类骨架，但需要完整实现来满足 spec 中定义的行为，包括镜像准备、双 provider 支持、前置校验、部署就绪等待和元数据更新。\n\n## 范围\n\n### 包含\n\n1. **`publish` Typer 命令实现** (`agentcube/cli/main.py`)\n   - 所有选项参数：`workspace` (`-f`, 默认 `.`), `version` (`--version`), `image_url` (`--image-url`), `image_username` (`--image-username`), `image_password` (`--image-password`), `description` (`--description`), `region` (`--region`), `cloud_provider` (`--cloud-provider`), `provider` (`--provider`, 默认 `\"agentcube\"`), `node_port` (`--node-port`, `Optional[int]`), `replicas` (`--replicas`), `namespace` (`--namespace`), `verbose` (`--verbose`)\n   - 成功输出：Rich 格式显示 provider 类型、部署名称、namespace、endpoint URL\n   - 错误处理：通过 `_handle_error(e, \"publish\", verbose)` 打印红色错误信息，verbose 时打印 traceback，退出码 1\n   - Rich `Progress` spinner 在执行期间显示\n\n2. **`PublishRuntime` 类完整实现** (`agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py`)\n   - `publish(workspace_path, **options)` — 主入口，编排完整发布流程\n   - `_prepare_image_for_publishing(workspace_path, metadata, options)` — 根据 build_mode 和 CLI 参数决定镜像来源，返回完整 image tag\n   - `_prepare_local_image(workspace_path, metadata, options)` — 本地模式：使用 `DockerService.push_image()` 推送到 registry，需要 `image_url`/`image_username`/`image_password`\n   - `_prepare_cloud_image(workspace_path, metadata, options)` — 云端模式：从 metadata 或 CLI 获取已有 image URL\n   - `_publish_cr_to_k8s(workspace_path, metadata, **options)` — AgentCube provider：使用 `AgentCubeProvider.deploy_agent_runtime()` 创建/更新 AgentRuntime CR，等待就绪\n   - `_publish_k8s(workspace_path, metadata, **options)` — 标准 K8s provider：使用 `KubernetesProvider.deploy_agent()` 创建 Deployment + NodePort Service，调用 `wait_for_deployment_ready(..., timeout=120)`\n   - `_update_publish_metadata(workspace_path, agent_info)` — 更新 metadata 的 `agent_id`、`agent_endpoint`、`k8s_deployment` 等字段并持久化\n\n3. **`AgentCubeProvider` 完整实现** (`agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py`)\n   - `deploy_agent_runtime(agent_name, image_url, port, entrypoint, env_vars, workload_manager_url, router_url, readiness_probe_path, readiness_probe_port)` — 创建/patch AgentRuntime CR\n   - CR API: `group=\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"`, `version=\"v1alpha1\"`, `plural=\"agentruntimes\"`\n   - 嵌入 `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` / `ROUTER_URL` 环境变量（优先参数，fallback 到系统环境变量）\n   - 设置 `sessionTimeout: \"15m\"`、`maxSessionDuration: \"8h\"`、`imagePullSecrets: [{\"name\": \"default-secret\"}]`\n   -  readiness probe 配置（当 metadata 中存在 readiness probe 字段时）\n   - `_sanitize_name(name)` — 名称合法化\n   - `_ensure_namespace()` — 确保 namespace 存在\n   - `get_agent_runtime(name, namespace)` — 查询 CR 状态\n\n4. **`KubernetesProvider` 完整实现** (`agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py`)\n   - `deploy_agent(agent_name, image_url, port, entrypoint, replicas, node_port, env_vars)` — 创建 Deployment + NodePort Service\n   - `_create_deployment(...)` — 创建或 patch Deployment\n   - `_create_service(name, port, node_port)` — 创建 NodePort Service\n   - `wait_for_deployment_ready(name, timeout=120)` — 轮询等待 Deployment 就绪，超时抛 `TimeoutError`\n   - `get_agent_status(agent_name)` — 查询 Deployment/Service/pod 状态\n   - `delete_agent(agent_name)` — 删除 Deployment + Service（忽略 404）\n   - `_sanitize_name(name)` — 名称合法化\n   - `_ensure_namespace()` — 确保 namespace 存在\n\n5. **`StatusRuntime` 状态查询增强** (`agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py`)\n   - `_get_cr_k8s_status(metadata)` — 读取 AgentRuntime CR 的 `status` 字段，返回 `status`/`agentEndpoint` 或 `created_no_status`/`not_found_in_k8s`\n\n### 不包含\n\n- `pack` / `build` 命令的实现（由 AR-020 / AR-021 覆盖）\n- `DockerService.build_image()` 的实现（由 AR-021 覆盖）\n- `invoke` 命令的完整实现（依赖 publish 输出的 endpoint，由其他 AR 覆盖）\n- Go 二进制入口 (`cmd/agentcube/`, `cmd/agentcube-controller/`) — 独立实现\n- CI/CD pipeline 变更\n- 云端构建的具体云厂商适配器实现\n\n## 架构概要\n\n### 组件关系\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    CLI Layer (Typer)                             │\n│  agentcube/cli/main.py: publish() command                        │\n│  - 解析选项 → 调用 PublishRuntime.publish()                      │\n│  - Rich 输出 / _handle_error()                                   │\n└──────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────┘\n                           │\n┌──────────────────────────▼──────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                     Runtime Layer                                │\n│  agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py: PublishRuntime            │\n│  - 镜像准备 → 前置校验 → 部署 → 元数据更新                       │\n│  - 根据 provider 分发到 AgentCubeProvider / KubernetesProvider   │\n│  - 依赖 DockerService 推送镜像（本地模式）                       │\n│  - 依赖 MetadataService 加载/保存元数据                          │\n└───┬──────────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────┘\n    │                              │\n┌───▼──────────────┐  ┌────────────▼──────────────────────────────┐\n│  Service Layer    │  │  Provider Layer                           │\n│  DockerService    │  │  ┌─────────────────┐ ┌─────────────────┐  │\n│  - push_image     │  │  │ AgentCubeProvider│ │KubernetesProvider│ │\n│  - docker_login   │  │  │ - AgentRuntime CR│ │- Deployment     │  │\n│  - tag_image      │  │  │ - group: runtime. │ │- NodePort Svc   │  │\n│  └───────────────┘  │  │   agentcube...   │ │- wait_for_ready │  │\n                      │  └─────────────────┘ └─────────────────┘  │\n                      └───────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n### 发布流程\n\n```\npublish() CLI\n  │\n  ├── PublishRuntime.publish()\n  │     │\n  │     ├── 1. 加载 agent_metadata.yaml\n  │     │\n  │     ├── 2. 合并 CLI 选项到 metadata（version, description, region 等）\n  │     │\n  │     ├── 3. _prepare_image_for_publishing()\n  │     │     ├── build_mode == \"local\" → _prepare_local_image()\n  │     │     │     └── DockerService.push_image(registry_url, username, password)\n  │     │     └── build_mode == \"cloud\" → _prepare_cloud_image()\n  │     │           └── 使用已有 image URL（从 metadata 或 CLI --image-url）\n  │     │\n  │     ├── 4. 根据 provider 分发\n  │     │     ├── \"agentcube\" → _publish_cr_to_k8s()\n  │     │     │     ├── 校验 router_url 和 workload_manager_url\n  │     │     │     └── AgentCubeProvider.deploy_agent_runtime()\n  │     │     │           └── 创建/patch AgentRuntime CR\n  │     │     └── \"k8s\" → _publish_k8s()\n  │     │           ├── KubernetesProvider.deploy_agent()\n  │     │           │     ├── _create_deployment()\n  │     │           │     └── _create_service()\n  │     │           └── wait_for_deployment_ready(timeout=120)\n  │     │\n  │     ├── 5. _update_publish_metadata()\n  │     │     └── 保存 agent_id, agent_endpoint, k8s_deployment\n  │     │\n  │     └── 6. 返回部署结果\n  │\n  └── CLI 输出: provider, deployment_name, namespace, endpoint\n```\n\n### 目录结构（新增/修改的文件）\n\n```\ncmd/cli/\n├── agentcube/\n│   ├── cli/\n│   │   └── main.py                    # 修改: 实现 publish() 命令体\n│   ├── runtime/\n│   │   └── publish_runtime.py         # 实现: PublishRuntime 类\n│   └── services/\n│       ├── agentcube_provider.py      # 实现: AgentCubeProvider 类\n│       └── k8s_provider.py            # 实现: KubernetesProvider 类\n```\n\n## 影响分析\n\n### 直接影响\n\n| 文件 | 变更类型 | 说明 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| `agentcube/cli/main.py` | 修改 | 实现 `publish()` 命令体，调用 `PublishRuntime` |\n| `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | 实现 | 完整实现所有方法 |\n| `agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py` | 实现 | AgentRuntime CR 的创建/patch/查询 |\n| `agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py` | 实现 | Deployment/Service 的创建/等待就绪/查询/删除 |\n| `agentcube/services/docker_service.py` | 确认 | 确保 `push_image` 支持 publish 场景 |\n| `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | 确认 | 确保 load/save 支持 publish 元数据字段 |\n| `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` | 确认 | `_get_cr_k8s_status` 依赖 publish 输出的 CR |\n\n### 上游依赖（本变更依赖的已完成组件）\n\n- **AR-020 (`pack` 命令)** — 依赖 pack 生成的 `agent_metadata.yaml`\n- **AR-021 (`build` 命令)** — 依赖 build 产出的容器镜像和更新后的 metadata.image\n- `typer[all]>=0.9.0` — CLI 框架（已有依赖）\n- `pydantic>=2.0.0` — 元数据验证（已有依赖）\n- `pyyaml>=6.0` — YAML 序列化（已有依赖）\n- `docker>=6.0.0` — Docker SDK for Python（已有依赖，本地 push 模式）\n- `rich>=13.0.0` — Progress spinner、Table 格式化输出（已有依赖）\n- `kubernetes>=28.0.0` — Kubernetes Python client（optional 依赖，publish/invoke/status 需要）\n- `httpx>=0.24.0` — HTTP 客户端（已有依赖）\n\n### 下游依赖（本变更完成后解锁）\n\n- **AR: `invoke` 命令** — 依赖 publish 部署后的 agent endpoint 进行调用\n- **AR: `status` 命令** — 依赖 publish 输出的 metadata 展示部署状态\n\n### 无影响的组件\n\n- `PackRuntime` / `BuildRuntime` — 本 AR 不修改 pack/build 逻辑\n- `InvokeRuntime` / `StatusRuntime` 的核心方法 — 仅确认现有接口兼容\n- Go 二进制入口 (`cmd/agentcube/`, `cmd/agentcube-controller/`) — 独立实现\n- Python SDK (`sdk-python/`) — 独立实现\n\n### 风险评估\n\n| 风险 | 等级 | 缓解措施 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| Kubernetes 集群不可达或 kubeconfig 配置错误 | 高 | `_ensure_namespace()` 提前验证连接，给出清晰的错误提示 |\n| AgentRuntime CR 部署后长时间未就绪 | 高 | 设置合理的超时等待（参考 K8s provider 的 120s timeout），超时后记录错误到 metadata |\n| 本地镜像推送失败（registry 认证/网络） | 高 | `_prepare_local_image` 中先执行 `DockerService._docker_login_sdk`，失败时给出明确指引 |\n| `router_url` 或 `workload_manager_url` 缺失导致 AgentCube 部署失败 | 中 | 前置校验在 `_publish_cr_to_k8s` 中检查，抛出 `ValueError` 要求配置 |\n| `node_port` 冲突（30000-32767 范围） | 中 | K8s 会拒绝冲突的 NodePort，捕获异常并提示用户更换 |\n| 镜像拉取失败（imagePullSecrets 配置不正确） | 中 | CR 中使用 `default-secret`，用户需提前配置；部署失败后通过 status 命令诊断 |\n| namespace 不存在导致部署失败 | 低 | `_ensure_namespace()` 自动创建 namespace |\n\n## 备选方案\n\n### 1. PublishRuntime 类编排所有发布步骤（✅ 选定方案）\n\n**做法**：`PublishRuntime` 类包含所有私有方法，在 `publish()` 中顺序调用，与 `PackRuntime` / `BuildRuntime` 模式一致。\n\n**优点**：\n- 与现有 `PackRuntime` / `BuildRuntime` 架构一致，降低认知负担\n- 逻辑集中，易于调试和测试\n- 与 spec 中定义的类结构完全匹配\n\n**缺点**：\n- 类包含多种职责（镜像准备、部署、元数据更新）\n- AgentCube CR 和标准 K8s 部署逻辑差异较大\n\n**决策**：采用。与现有 spec 和架构一致，通过 provider 参数分发到不同的 Provider 类，保持职责分离。\n\n### 2. 部署策略模式分离 AgentCube / K8s\n\n**做法**：定义 `DeployStrategy` 接口，`AgentCubeDeployStrategy` 和 `K8sDeployStrategy` 实现，`PublishRuntime` 委托给策略。\n\n**优点**：\n- 两种部署逻辑完全隔离\n- 添加新 provider（如 AWS ECS、GCP Cloud Run）只需新策略\n\n**缺点**：\n- 增加抽象层，对当前仅 2 种 provider 来说过度设计\n- 与 spec 中定义的 `_publish_cr_to_k8s` / `_publish_k8s` 私有方法结构不一致\n\n**决策**：不采用。当前仅支持 agentcube/k8s，策略模式增加复杂度。Provider 层已通过 `AgentCubeProvider` / `KubernetesProvider` 实现职责分离。可在未来添加第 3 种 provider 时重构。\n\n### 3. 镜像准备与部署分离为两个命令\n\n**做法**：将 `publish` 拆分为 `push`（仅推送镜像）和 `deploy`（仅部署资源）两个命令。\n\n**优点**：\n- 职责更清晰，用户可以单独推送镜像或单独部署\n- 支持跨环境复用同一镜像（push 一次，deploy 多次）\n\n**缺点**：\n- 与 spec 中单一 `publish` 命令的设计不符\n- 增加用户学习成本（需要理解两个命令的关系）\n- 当前用户场景是\"一次发布完成所有步骤\"\n\n**决策**：不采用。遵循 spec 中 `publish` 命令的单一入口设计。内部通过 `_prepare_image_for_publishing` 和 `_publish_cr_to_k8s` / `_publish_k8s` 实现逻辑分离。\n\n## 实现要点\n\n### `publish` 命令流程\n\n```python\n@app.command()\ndef publish(\n    workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\", ...),\n    version: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--version\", ...),\n    image_url: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--image-url\", ...),\n    image_username: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--image-username\", ...),\n    image_password: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--image-password\", ...),\n    description: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--description\", ...),\n    region: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--region\", ...),\n    cloud_provider: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--cloud-provider\", ...),\n    provider: str = typer.Option(\"agentcube\", \"--provider\", ...),\n    node_port: Optional[int] = typer.Option(None, \"--node-port\", ...),\n    replicas: Optional[int] = typer.Option(None, \"--replicas\", ...),\n    namespace: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--namespace\", ...),\n    verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\", ...),\n) -> None:\n    workspace_path = Path(workspace).resolve()\n    try:\n        with Progress() as progress:\n            task = progress.add_task(\"Publishing...\", total=None)\n            runtime = PublishRuntime(verbose=verbose, provider=provider)\n            result = runtime.publish(\n                workspace_path,\n                version=version,\n                image_url=image_url,\n                image_username=image_username,\n                image_password=image_password,\n                description=description,\n                region=region,\n                cloud_provider=cloud_provider,\n                node_port=node_port,\n                replicas=replicas,\n                namespace=namespace,\n            )\n        # Rich 输出: provider, deployment_name, namespace, endpoint\n    except Exception as e:\n        _handle_error(e, \"publish\", verbose)\n```\n\n### `PublishRuntime.publish()` 内部流程\n\n```python\ndef publish(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n    # 1. 加载元数据\n    metadata = self.metadata_service.load_metadata(workspace_path)\n\n    # 2. 合并 CLI 选项\n    if options.get(\"version\"):\n        metadata.version = options[\"version\"]\n    if options.get(\"description\"):\n        metadata.description = options[\"description\"]\n    if options.get(\"region\"):\n        metadata.region = options[\"region\"]\n    if options.get(\"namespace\"):\n        self.namespace = options[\"namespace\"]\n\n    # 3. 准备镜像\n    image_tag = self._prepare_image_for_publishing(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n\n    # 4. 根据 provider 分发\n    if self.provider == \"agentcube\":\n        agent_info = self._publish_cr_to_k8s(workspace_path, metadata, **options)\n    else:\n        agent_info = self._publish_k8s(workspace_path, metadata, **options)\n\n    # 5. 更新元数据\n    self._update_publish_metadata(workspace_path, agent_info)\n\n    return agent_info\n```\n\n### 镜像准备 — 本地模式\n\n```python\ndef _prepare_local_image(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> str:\n    docker_service = DockerService(verbose=self.verbose)\n\n    registry_url = options.get(\"image_url\") or metadata.registry_url or metadata.image.get(\"name\")\n    username = options.get(\"image_username\") or metadata.registry_username\n    password = options.get(\"image_password\") or metadata.registry_password\n\n    if not registry_url:\n        raise ValueError(\"--image-url is required in local build mode\")\n\n    tag = metadata.version or \"latest\"\n    source_image = f\"{metadata.image.get('name', metadata.agent_name)}:{tag}\"\n\n    # 推送镜像\n    push_result = docker_service.push_image(\n        image_name=source_image,\n        registry_url=registry_url,\n        username=username,\n        password=password,\n    )\n\n    return push_result[\"pushed_image\"]\n```\n\n### 镜像准备 — 云端模式\n\n```python\ndef _prepare_cloud_image(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> str:\n    image_url = options.get(\"image_url\")\n    if image_url:\n        return image_url\n\n    if metadata.image and metadata.image.get(\"name\"):\n        tag = metadata.version or \"latest\"\n        return f\"{metadata.image['name']}:{tag}\"\n\n    raise ValueError(\"Image URL not found. Specify --image-url or ensure metadata.image is set.\")\n```\n\n### AgentCube CR 部署\n\n```python\ndef _publish_cr_to_k8s(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n    # 前置校验\n    if not metadata.router_url:\n        raise ValueError(\n            \"router_url is required for AgentCube provider. \"\n            \"Set it in agent_metadata.yaml or via CLI options.\"\n        )\n    if not metadata.workload_manager_url:\n        raise ValueError(\n            \"workload_manager_url is required for AgentCube provider. \"\n            \"Set it in agent_metadata.yaml or via CLI options.\"\n        )\n\n    provider = AgentCubeProvider(\n        namespace=self.namespace,\n        verbose=self.verbose,\n    )\n\n    result = provider.deploy_agent_runtime(\n        agent_name=metadata.agent_name,\n        image_url=self._prepare_image_for_publishing(workspace_path, metadata, options),\n        port=metadata.port,\n        entrypoint=metadata.entrypoint,\n        env_vars=None,\n        workload_manager_url=metadata.workload_manager_url,\n        router_url=metadata.router_url,\n        readiness_probe_path=metadata.readiness_probe_path,\n        readiness_probe_port=metadata.readiness_probe_port,\n    )\n\n    return {\n        \"provider\": \"agentcube\",\n        \"agent_name\": metadata.agent_name,\n        \"namespace\": self.namespace,\n        \"cr_name\": result.get(\"cr_name\", metadata.agent_name),\n        \"status\": result.get(\"status\", \"created\"),\n    }\n```\n\n### 标准 K8s 部署\n\n```python\ndef _publish_k8s(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n    provider = KubernetesProvider(\n        namespace=self.namespace,\n        verbose=self.verbose,\n    )\n\n    image_tag = self._prepare_image_for_publishing(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n    replicas = options.get(\"replicas\") or 1\n    node_port = options.get(\"node_port\")\n\n    result = provider.deploy_agent(\n        agent_name=metadata.agent_name,\n        image_url=image_tag,\n        port=metadata.port,\n        entrypoint=metadata.entrypoint,\n        replicas=replicas,\n        node_port=node_port,\n        env_vars=None,\n    )\n\n    # 等待部署就绪\n    try:\n        provider.wait_for_deployment_ready(result[\"deployment_name\"], timeout=120)\n        result[\"status\"] = \"ready\"\n    except TimeoutError:\n        result[\"status\"] = \"error\"\n        result[\"error\"] = \"Deployment did not become ready within 120 seconds\"\n        # 记录错误到 metadata\n        metadata.k8s_deployment = result\n        self.metadata_service.save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)\n        raise RuntimeError(result[\"error\"])\n\n    return result\n```\n\n### `AgentCubeProvider.deploy_agent_runtime()` 关键实现\n\n```python\ndef deploy_agent_runtime(\n    self, agent_name, image_url, port, entrypoint=None,\n    env_vars=None, workload_manager_url=None, router_url=None,\n    readiness_probe_path=None, readiness_probe_port=None,\n) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n    self._ensure_namespace()\n    sanitized_name = self._sanitize_name(agent_name)\n\n    # 构建 CR 对象\n    cr_body = {\n        \"apiVersion\": \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\",\n        \"kind\": \"AgentRuntime\",\n        \"metadata\": {\"name\": sanitized_name, \"namespace\": self.namespace},\n        \"spec\": {\n            \"image\": image_url,\n            \"port\": port,\n            \"sessionTimeout\": \"15m\",\n            \"maxSessionDuration\": \"8h\",\n            \"imagePullSecrets\": [{\"name\": \"default-secret\"}],\n            \"env\": [],\n        },\n    }\n\n    # 环境变量\n    env_list = list(env_vars.items()) if env_vars else []\n    wm_url = workload_manager_url or os.environ.get(\"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\", \"\")\n    r_url = router_url or os.environ.get(\"ROUTER_URL\", \"\")\n    if wm_url:\n        env_list.append({\"name\": \"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\", \"value\": wm_url})\n    if r_url:\n        env_list.append({\"name\": \"ROUTER_URL\", \"value\": r_url})\n    if env_list:\n        cr_body[\"spec\"][\"env\"] = env_list\n\n    # Readiness probe\n    if readiness_probe_path and readiness_probe_port:\n        cr_body[\"spec\"][\"readinessProbe\"] = {\n            \"httpGet\": {\"path\": readiness_probe_path, \"port\": readiness_probe_port},\n        }\n\n    # 创建或 patch\n    try:\n        existing = self.get_agent_runtime(sanitized_name, self.namespace)\n        if existing:\n            # Patch\n            self.custom_objects.patch_namespaced_custom_object(\n                group=\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\",\n                version=\"v1alpha1\",\n                namespace=self.namespace,\n                plural=\"agentruntimes\",\n                name=sanitized_name,\n                body=cr_body,\n            )\n        else:\n            self.custom_objects.create_namespaced_custom_object(\n                group=\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\",\n                version=\"v1alpha1\",\n                namespace=self.namespace,\n                plural=\"agentruntimes\",\n                body=cr_body,\n            )\n    except Exception as e:\n        raise RuntimeError(f\"Failed to deploy AgentRuntime CR: {e}\")\n\n    return {\"cr_name\": sanitized_name, \"namespace\": self.namespace, \"status\": \"created\"}\n```\n\n### `KubernetesProvider.wait_for_deployment_ready()` 实现\n\n```python\ndef wait_for_deployment_ready(self, name: str, timeout: int = 120) -> None:\n    start = time.time()\n    while time.time() - start < timeout:\n        try:\n            deployment = self.apps_v1.read_namespaced_deployment(name, self.namespace)\n            if (\n                deployment.status.ready_replicas\n                and deployment.status.ready_replicas == deployment.spec.replicas\n            ):\n                return\n        except ApiException:\n            pass\n        time.sleep(2)\n    raise TimeoutError(\n        f\"Deployment {name} did not become ready within {timeout} seconds\"\n    )\n```\n\n### `_update_publish_metadata()` 实现\n\n```python\ndef _update_publish_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, agent_info: Dict[str, Any]) -> None:\n    metadata = self.metadata_service.load_metadata(workspace_path)\n\n    metadata.agent_id = agent_info.get(\"agent_name\") or agent_info.get(\"deployment_name\")\n    metadata.k8s_deployment = {\n        \"type\": \"AgentRuntime\" if agent_info.get(\"provider\") == \"agentcube\" else \"Deployment\",\n        \"name\": agent_info.get(\"cr_name\") or agent_info.get(\"deployment_name\"),\n        \"namespace\": agent_info.get(\"namespace\"),\n    }\n\n    # 构建 endpoint URL\n    if agent_info.get(\"provider\") == \"k8s\" and agent_info.get(\"service_url\"):\n        metadata.agent_endpoint = agent_info[\"service_url\"]\n    elif agent_info.get(\"provider\") == \"agentcube\":\n        # CR 部署后 endpoint 由 Router 提供，初始为占位\n        metadata.agent_endpoint = None\n\n    self.metadata_service.save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)\n```\n\n## 验收标准\n\n- [ ] `publish` 命令接受所有指定选项，使用正确默认值\n- [ ] `workspace` 默认 `.`，可通过 `-f` / `--workspace` 覆盖\n- [ ] `provider` 默认 `\"agentcube\"`，可通过 `--provider` 切换为 `\"k8s\"`\n- [ ] AgentCube provider：metadata 缺少 `router_url` 或 `workload_manager_url` 时抛出 `ValueError`\n- [ ] AgentCube provider：创建/patch AgentRuntime CR 到 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/agentruntimes`\n- [ ] AgentCube provider：CR 包含 `sessionTimeout: \"15m\"`、`maxSessionDuration: \"8h\"`、`imagePullSecrets`\n- [ ] AgentCube provider：环境变量嵌入 `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` / `ROUTER_URL`（参数优先，fallback 到环境变量）\n- [ ] K8s provider：创建 Deployment + NodePort Service\n- [ ] K8s provider：调用 `wait_for_deployment_ready(..., timeout=120)`，超时抛 `RuntimeError`\n- [ ] K8s provider：`--replicas` 控制副本数，`--node-port` 指定 NodePort（30000-32767）\n- [ ] K8s provider：`--namespace` 控制部署 namespace\n- [ ] 本地 build 模式：`--image-url` 为必需参数，使用 `DockerService.push_image()` 推送\n- [ ] 云端 build 模式：使用已有 image URL（metadata 或 `--image-url`）\n- [ ] 发布成功后更新 `metadata.agent_id`、`metadata.agent_endpoint`、`metadata.k8s_deployment`\n- [ ] 发布失败时记录错误到 metadata 并抛出异常\n- [ ] 成功消息显示 provider 类型、部署名称、namespace、endpoint（Rich 格式）\n- [ ] 错误处理打印红色消息 + traceback（verbose），退出码 1\n- [ ] Rich `Progress` spinner 在执行期间显示\n- [ ] `--verbose` 启用详细日志输出\n- [ ] `--version` 选项覆盖 metadata 中的版本号\n- [ ] `--description` 和 `--region` 选项更新 metadata 对应字段\n- [ ] `status` 命令能正确读取 AgentRuntime CR 的 status 字段\n\n## 状态\n\n- [ ] 提案审查\n- [ ] 实现\n- [ ] 验证\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/proposal.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/proposal.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775853822058,"end":1775853822084}}}}
